title: 2013-14 patch (v1.2.5) for FIFA 11 - FIF14 faces
description:
2013-14 patch (v1.2.5) for FIFA 11

included:

- FIFA 11 Selector:
* fix: cant move read-only files
* databases: error/speed improvements
* New: players - change sleeves, tucked, undershorts, tight kits, sock, winter accs, shoes, ...
* New: Tattoos - enable/disable function
* New: Support > Help - list errors & common problems
* New: Support > Performance optimizer 

- Squads
* updated squads (date: 02.05.14)

- Faces
New faces: all new fifa online 3 faces (= FIFA 14 faces)
* fifa 14 faces + exclusive fifa online 3 faces (junazaj, isco, ...) 
* old (bad) faces removed
* generic faces: improved (fifa online 3)

- New added: tight kits
* + player assignments

- New added: sock heights
* high, normal, low socks
* + player assignments

- body 
new body-models (fifa online 3)
* arms, legs, ...
* improved skin colours

- jerseys
new jersey (kit)-models (fifa online 3)

- tattoos:
* turn on/off with selector (off by default)

- New shoes + updated assignments
* adidas F50 adiZero XTRX Synthetic - Crazylight
* adidas Predator LZ II - White/Orange/Black
* adidas F50 adiZero XTRX Synthetic - Glow Earth Earth Green Solar Zest
* Umbro Geoflare - Orange/Black
* Umbro Geoflare - Black/Orange/White
* Umbro Geoflare - White/Blue/Red
* Nike Mercurial Vapor IX - MetallicMatchPurple Black TotalOrange
* Nike Mercurial Vapor IX - MetallicMatchPurple Black TotalOrange - CR7
* Pele Sports Trinity 3E - BlackGreyOrange
* Pele Sports Trinity 3E - BlackYellow
* Umbro Speciali IV - BlueWhiteRed
* Umbro Speciali IV - Orange
* Umbro Speciali IV - White
* Umbro Speciali IV - Yellow
+ Updates

- balls
* updated (to fifa 14 models): nike incyte balls
* new balls: Derbystar (dutch eredivisie) 

- mini faces:
* updates

- accessories
* winter accessories: undershorts enabled
* wrist accessories: removed when long sleeves

- Real Performance Optimizer
* reduce FIFA 11 lags
* at menu's & during gameplay
* turn on/off with selector (on by default)

- lua files (fifa 11 prgm code):
* improvements
* new features added
* fix: crash when new teams added
* fix: tattoos


2013-14 patch (v1.2) INCLUDED in this release 

Supported languages english, Czech, dutch, french, german, italian, spanish (2X), portuguese, polish, Russian




Supported languages english, Czech, dutch, french, german, italian, spanish (2X), portuguese, polish, Russian



Installation:
1. install fifa 11 
2. install ea patch (1.01)
3. install 2013-14 patch (v1.1.0)

4. install 2013-14 patch (v1.2.5)


Notes
- patch v1.1.0 NEEDED, later patches are included
- will overwrite current database (squads)
- to continue career-savegames: make backup (selector) before install




pls leave your comments if there are any problems
